<br>
If I have the place to myself, then with aggressive petcanni and modrod use, I can easily hold every dryad spawn near the Brell caves -- about 11 spawn points every 6 minutes.  This translates to slightly over 1 blue every hour or so.<br>
<br>
Some of them are light blue, but most are dk blue at 56.  If you get reasonable luck with drops, you can do about 300pp per 2-3 hours spent here.  Nothing to write home about, but enough to keep me interested.<br>
<br>
At 57, these won't be worth the time, though. <br>
