<br>
Its an easy camp and I would start at cave entrance and fight my way to wherever I wanted then work my way back towards entrance over and over.<br>
<br>
I would bind near the port out area just in case. Inner zone gate and click on gem if needed.<br>
<br>
I would pull with malosi or a ceramic band. I would armor up pet and give full set of foci so I didn't need to chain...but then I do have the epic pet, though i did try this with water and it worked well.<br>
<br>
Edge into sight of room along wall. <br>
Target Closest gnoll.<br>
Cast ring or malosi.<br>
Move back to middle of hall.<br>
When gnoll gets close sic pet on it.<br>
Rain once &amp; heal pet if needed. usually once.<br>
Rinse / Repeat.<br>
<br>
Was pretty easy to go from front cave all the way to back cave or any side cave.  If you get into barduks room you can litterly work your way around the edge of the room with little to no problem. The gnolls are far enough apart to pull at 55-56 with no adds.<br>
